== Notes ==
* A brand new custom land mass introduced in April 2015.
* Located just east of New [[Magincia]]. The island can be access via a tunnel on the east side of New [[Magincia]], by boat or by simply recalling in!
* This is a no mount area.
* Player housing can be placed here.
* There are several creature spawns including:
** Silver serpent, [[Tameables#Swamp_Dragon|Swamp Dragon]], Titan, Ogre Lord, Harpy, Drake, Dragon, Pirate
* There is a [[Booty_Island_Dungeon|dungeon]] on an island off the north east side of the main land.
